data.description: Fantastic views of the Superstition Mountains in this luxurious home with  a 3-car detached garage/casita (with running water and room for a bed and furniture. Approx 1600 sq ft) Parking and electric/sewer for two RV's and multiple parking spaces outside. The gated courtyard boasts multiple eating areas and artificial turf. Inside you'll be welcomed by a living room boasting high ceilings, abundant natural light, and a harmonious blend of soft carpet and tile flooring. Dining room, complete with a wet bar. Gorgeous kitchen, featuring granite counters, ample cabinetry with crown molding, recessed lighting, matching appliances, a pantry, and an island with a breakfast bar. Full backyard kitchen and separate storage unit in the back. Construction is concrete steel and foam. Built to last! \The main bedroom is a serene retreat, private outdoor access, a walk-in closet, and an ensuite with dual vanities. Venture into the backyard oasis, showcasing a patio for outdoor relaxation, a built-in BBQ, a tranquil pond, a detached workshop, and a lovely ramada. This gem will sell fast! Act now before it's gone!
